                    <td>Yeah, kartoffel's got it wrong, or he was bugged that day.  

Mez a mob and keep singing.  You can target anything else and that first mob will stay mezzed, so long as no resists.  

If you sing a song, though, you'll  have to retarget to mez.

Kurlie has the right idea.  With 1 mob, I'll &quot;pivot&quot; target on that mob for the mez, then I'll assist the MT to get agro back on the mob to melee, sing 2 or 3 battle songs, then pivot back and remez.

For 2 mobs either concentrate on mezzing ...</td>
